name: Twelve Days of CryptoArt by UltraDAO

metadata.name: ForgetCode by Shunsuke Takawo
metadata.description:
*ForgetCode Instruction*

1) Complete the code in 60 minutes. 
2) Export the graphics. 
3) Discard the code. 

Daily coding is a process of writing, composing, and binding code. This time, however, I had 60 minutes to write code and then delete it to complete my work. As a result, I will never be able to recreate the details of this code. I wanted to include a sense of wabi in the code I would write as I expected to part with it all.
